README
===

To build:

	docker build -t piwik .

To run:

	export HOSTIP=`ip -4 addr show scope global dev eth0 | grep inet | awk '{print \$2}' | cut -d / -f 1` && \
		docker run -p 127.0.0.1:9999:80 --add-host=docker:${HOSTIP} piwik

This will expose the app just on the local network, and then Apache can be
used on the host to proxy it to the outside world.
